{"tid":1643220,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【大國風範？】Converse出「中國」鞋被大讚 網民FC竟係越南風","createTime":"2019-10-10T04:42:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T19:31:52.000Z","uid":28765,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"59c8ec1a2b19a6377e51efb81ba551d42797f0a1","tid":1643220,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T04:42:34.000Z","msg":"6小時前<br />\n即時兩岸<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191009/large/1570628436_1a0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191009%2Flarge%2F1570628436_1a0d.jpg&h=2a8fbc18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191009/large/1570635962_a1cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191009%2Flarge%2F1570635962_a1cb.jpg&h=506d6cad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n知名的波鞋品牌，近年都會出特別設計的款式，吸引消費者購買，早前Converse推出多款新設計的帆布鞋及外套，用色、花紋都極像古裝劇內人物的服裝，內地網民看到照片後，大讚這些「中國風」十分親切。不過，有網民查證時發現，這些帆布鞋都是越南的設計，外套更是「越南日平襖」。<br />\n<br />\nConverse上月底在網上公開這6款帆布鞋，旋即被網民不斷轉載，在網上成為熱門話題。有網民稱，近年很多外國品牌都參考中國的設計，所以Converse這次也是「跟風」，參考中國古代的設計。網民更將紅色稱為「中國紅」、黃色是「皇室專用正統黃」，還大讚這些「中國風帆布鞋」，穿上後「可以登基」、「揚我大國風範」、「成為時尚icon就靠這鞋了」。<br />\n<br />\n在網民為這幾雙帆布鞋瘋狂的時候，有網民仔細追查，竟然發現這幾款鞋根本不是「中國風」，而是「越南風」，外套不是清朝的衣服，而是「越南日平襖」，並且與越南著名時裝品牌BARO，合作出推名為「Annam Heritage」系列產品。弄了這麼大的笑話，讓很多原來追捧的網民即時崩潰，已經沒再討論這批帆布鞋。<br />\n<br />\n這事件讓很多追捧外國品牌中國風設計的網民，再次反思近年各國品牌追捧中國設計：「究竟甚麼是『國風』，其實大多數人都說不清楚，就連很多大品牌也迷迷糊糊、雲裏霧裏，最後弄巧成拙。」「各種國外大牌都爭先恐後地推出『奇葩』新年限定款，無一例外都因水土不服，遭網民群嘲！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191010/60135136\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191010%2F60135136&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2Em0oInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=21271bab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191010%2F60135136&h=15ae0957\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191010/60135136</a>"},{"pid":"a3d333c0948fd2ace6e2c3b16e17972d0aeed834","tid":1643220,"uid":66822,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T04:43:47.000Z","msg":"星期五中環快閃 撐被捕保安<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FoM1jNJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFoM1jNJ.jpg&h=eaa6b73f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7onWS7K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7onWS7K.jpg&h=4e446c9d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38ba8db42be556843dc24dc9486b26198858df22","tid":1643220,"uid":128569,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T04:44:12.000Z","msg":"其實幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcfa80262f7e2cb1820a831690a2ce7e39c8102c","tid":1643220,"uid":277235,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T04:45:46.000Z","msg":"成日話愛国愛国，但其實国係點都唔知"},{"pid":"81d272c25fdbda1ae8837df37fe0785736f2ef8a","tid":1643220,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T04:45:54.000Z","msg":"留名等睇抵制越南"},{"pid":"e894d409a6ce9c01768db7d05fbf3f797936e4ba","tid":1643220,"uid":54126,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T04:47:27.000Z","msg":"支那蝗又柒出國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"930d175fdadfafe08cb96095f1189239459723bc","tid":1643220,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T04:48:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fjVxrxd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfjVxrxd.jpg&h=6fcc1a4c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e04b50deea1f07d714c1ca93f250bab034005a05","tid":1643220,"uid":249160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor